<node CREATED="1668947425435" ID="ID_667302992" MODIFIED="1668947434984">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      MCAL
    </p>
    AUTOSAR is a standardized automotive software architecture that facilitates the exchange and update of software and hardware throughout a vehicle&#8217;s service life. It enables a transition from an ECU-specific software development to an application-oriented approach.

    <p>
      <br http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
      ST provides a full set of software components for the AUTOSAR Microcontroller Abstraction Layer (MCAL) in addition to Complex Device Drivers (CDD) to support specific hardware peripherals.<br />With the provided software components (CDD and MCAL drivers), a system supplier can use one set of standardized basic software drivers over different applications within one configuration tool.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
